OL,5, Almost 1.8 million children missed at  
OL,6, least 10% of school in the autumn term 
OL,7, in England, according to new estimates.
OL,9,FThe number of children missing at least
OL,10,Fhalf of school is also greater than    
OL,11,Fpreviously thought, at 122,000.        
OL,13,FThe figures are based on information   
OL,14,Fgathered from 145 councils for the     
OL,15,FChildren's Commissioner.               
OL,17,FDame Rachel de Souza said urgent action
OL,18,Fwas needed to identify the children    
OL,19,Fmost at risk, and the reasons why they 
OL,20,Fmiss school.                           
